---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy policy — Solana Toolbox" description="Privacy policy for Solana Toolbox.">
  <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Privacy policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Solana Toolbox is a static directory site. We do not collect personal information, require
        accounts, or store any user data on our servers.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white pt-4">Analytics</h2>

      <p>
        This site uses Google Analytics 4 (GA4) to understand how visitors use the site. GA4
        collects anonymised usage data including pages visited, time on site, browser type, and
        approximate location (country/region level). This data is processed by Google and subject
        to <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#14F195] hover:underline">Google's privacy policy</a>.
      </p>

      <p>
        We do not use this data to identify individuals. To opt out of Google Analytics across all
        sites, you can install the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#14F195] hover:underline">Google Analytics opt-out browser add-on</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white pt-4">External links</h2>

      <p>
        This site links to third-party tools and services. We are not responsible for the privacy
        practices of those sites. Check their respective privacy policies before using them.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white pt-4">Cookies</h2>

      <p>
        GA4 sets cookies to distinguish visitors and sessions. No other cookies are set by this
        site.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white pt-4">Contact</h2>

      <p>
        Questions about this policy can be raised via
        <a href="https://github.com/monkeybusiness-xyz/solana-toolbox/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#14F195] hover:underline">GitHub Issues</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
